title: Natives trade D-man, Kings acquire one
text:

The Neepawa Natives sent 18-year-old defenceman Terrance McLean to the English River Miners of the Superior International Junior Hockey League for future considerations. McLean had an assist and four penalty minutes in four games with the Natives.
